s://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYy385jo.jpg&h=5ec04895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【5】滿意就一路清新手任務一邊拎報酬強化隊伍,繼續推主線完成Normal第4章<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/hxUewAR.jpg\" /><br />\n【6】然後開始刷每日素材本,限時活動及周末寶珠關卡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">オトモン属性耐性表</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.altema.jp/mhr/zokusei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.altema.jp%2Fmhr%2Fzokusei.jpg&h=3c1cd68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"blue\">升LV70必要寶玉/禮物數</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgoFCix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgoFCix.jpg&h=61cbe401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">【常見問題】</span></span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"navy\"><strong>◆護符有咩用,買左加護LV都唔升◆</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M4nP8BF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM4nP8BF.jpg&h=b952f4de&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n各都市加護LV需要一定經驗值先會升,<br />\n而經驗值就係你BOX入面所有相對都市人既合計LV+合計護符數量,<br />\n人每升1LV=1EXP<br />\n護符1個=1EXP<br />\n所以護符買左就OK,咩都唔洗做"},{"pid":"dcd1fe7e5e6662f4ebfa587227bd04ce561c2737","tid":2125270,"uid":251188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"E巴開左就去佢度"}],"pinned":{"pid":"dcd1fe7e5e6662f4ebfa587227bd04ce561c2737","tid":2125270,"uid":251188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"E巴開左就去佢度"}}